metadata.name: Inhuman Noun - Loner
metadata.description:
Loner, a cool looking guy who volunteered himself in the discovery of forbidden science that is shunned in an era of absolute togetherness, the suffering of a love story becomes the forerunner to the creation of an eternal human who encourages loneliness.

Legend says, when you lose all sense of self, the bonds of a thousand chains will disappear. Lose yourself completely, go back to the roots of your own soul.

The Decalogy of modified human invention, An era where eternal life is a wild choice.
